* This skill is a reference to the quote "By Grabthar's hammer, by the sons of Worvan, you shall be avenged" from the film [[wikipedia:Galaxy Quest|Galaxy Quest]] ([http://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/comments/uodjr/im_a_guild_wars_2_developer_ama_about_the_next/c4x7sqc?context=3 source]).

