{{redirect 2|"FH"|the outpost|[[Fishermen's Haven]]}} {{Skill infobox | name = "Finish Him!" | id = 2353 | campaign = Eye of the North | attribute = Norn rank | type = Shout | energy = 10 | recharge = 15 | pve-only = y | target = foes | range = Casting | causes1 = Cracked Armor | causes2 = Deep Wound | description = [[Shout]]. If [[target]] [[foe]] has less than 50% [[Health]], that foe takes {{gr2|44|80}} [[damage]] and suffers from [[Cracked Armor]] and a [[Deep Wound]] for {{gr2|12|20}} seconds. | concise description = Shout. Deals {{gr2|44|80}} damage and inflicts Cracked Armor and Deep Wound conditions ({{gr2|12|20}} seconds). {{gray|No effect unless target foe has less than 50% Health.}} }}
{{Skill progression max10 |title track = [[Norn rank]] |var1 name = [[Damage]] |var1 at0 = 44 |var1 at10 = 80 |var2 name = [[Cracked Armor]] and [[Deep Wound]] [[duration]] |var2 at0 = 12 |var2 at10 = 20 }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]s''' * [[Final Round: Fight!]] ([[Gunnar's Hold]])
== Notes == * Unlike all other skills that inflict Deep Wound, the damage is dealt after Deep Wound is applied, so using "Finish Him!" on a near-death target will usually kill it. *Cracked armor [[cover]]s deep wound. {{bug|This skill ignores the effects of skills that provide health bonuses, such as [[Endure Pain]], when calculating 50% of the health; the target's health needs to be 50% of what it would be ''without'' the bonus.}}
== Trivia == * This skill's name is a reference to the video game [[wikipedia:Mortal Kombat|Mortal Kombat]] ([http://wiki.guildwars.com/index.php?title=User_talk:Emily_Diehl/Trivia_archive&oldid=312796#.22Finish_Him.21.22 source]). * The female in the [[skill icon]] appears to be [[Jora]]. * The male in the skill icon seems to be wearing [[Warrior Elite Gladiator armor|Elite Gladiator armor]].
{{DEFAULTSORT:Finish Him!}} [[Category:References to video games]]

{{pveversion|"For Great Justice!"}}
{{Skill infobox | name = "For Great Justice!" (PvP) | id = 2883 | campaign = Core | profession = Warrior | type = Shout | energy = 5 | recharge = 45 | causes1 = Adrenaline Gain | description = [[Shout]]. For 8 seconds, when you hit with an [[attack]], you gain 1 additional strike of [[adrenaline]]. | concise description = Shout. (8 seconds.) You gain 1 extra strike of adrenaline whenever you hit with an attack. | is-pvp = y | aoe = None }}
== Trivia == * The phrase "for great justice" comes from the English (European) translation of the video game [[w:Zero_Wing|Zero Wing]], which is also the source of the [["Make Your Time!"]] skill name and the "[[w:All your base are belong to us|All your base are belong to us]]" phrase.
