{{pveversion|"Go for the Eyes!"}} {{Skill infobox | id = 3026 | name = "Go for the Eyes!" (PvP) | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Paragon | attribute = Command | type = Shout | adrenaline = 4 | recharge = 4 | causes1 = Critical Hit | description = [[Shout]]. For 10 seconds, the next time each [[ally]] within [[earshot]] makes an [[attack]], that attack has an additional {{gr|30|75}}% chance to [[critical hit|critical]]. | concise description = Shout. (10 seconds.) Allies in earshot have +{{gr|30|75}}% to land a critical hit with their next attack. | is-pvp = y }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Command]] | var1 name = + Chance % | var1 at0 = 30 | var1 at15 = 75}}
==Notes== * This skill combines well with [[Keen Arrow (PvP)]], [[Vicious Attack]] and [["Find Their Weakness!" (PvP)]]. * Works well in [[Party|parties]] with [[minion]]s as all the minions are affected.
==Trivia== *The skill name derives from a quote by [[w:Minsc|Minsc]] (from the RPG Baldur's Gate) regarding his miniature giant space hamster Boo, in which he urges: "Go for the eyes, Boo, GO FOR THE EYES!" *The [[skill icon]] resembles the [http://www.guildwars.com/products/guildwars/gallery/poster/e3_2003.php poster art]. {{DEFAULTSORT:Go for the Eyes!}} [[Category:Skills that affect allies]]
[[de:"Zielt auf die Augen!" (PvP)]]

{{Skill infobox | id = 1558 | name = "Go for the Eyes!" | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Paragon | attribute = Command | type = Shout | adrenaline = 4 | causes1 = Critical Hit | description = [[Shout]]. For 10 seconds, the next time each [[ally]] within [[earshot]] makes an [[attack]], that attack has an additional {{gr|30|100}}% chance to [[critical hit|critical]]. | concise description = Shout. (10 seconds.) Allies in earshot have +{{gr|30|100}}% to land a critical hit with their next attack. | has-pvp = y }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Command]] | var1 name = + Chance % | var1 at0 = 30 | var1 at15 = 100}}
==Acquisition== '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' *[[Medando]] ([[Yohlon Haven]]) *[[Wedende]] ([[Dajkah Inlet]])
==Notes == * This skill is a staple [[energy management]] skill for primary paragons, even at 0 command, as it allows to trigger the [[Leadership]]'s energy gain effect frequently and without halting attacks. ** It can also indirectly help primary [[Assassin]]s via [[Critical Strikes]]. * This skill can help party members to meet the critical hit-dependent effects of skills such as [[Keen Arrow]]. * Assuming a mastery rank of 12 (roughly a 12% critical chance), rank 13 command is enough to guarantee a critical hit with this skill. * As with most skills affecting the next attack, this shout will affect attacks already in-flight when used. * The shout seems to end before the attack hits, triggering relevant [[Echo (skill type)|Finale]]s before the attack connects, but [[Soldier's Strike]] is still unblockable. {{anomaly|Contrary to what the description suggests, this skill triggers on hit rather than on attack. For instance, if [[Cyclone Axe]] hits several foes, only one of them has increased chance to be critically hit.}}
== Trivia == * The skill name is based on the oft-repeated battle cry of [[w:Minsc|Minsc]] in the RPG game, [[w:Baldur's Gate|Baldur's Gate]], which itself is an homage to the 1981 film, [[w:Clash_of_the_Titans_(1981_film)|Clash of the Titans]]. ([http://youtu.be/X8lLruVR2zQ Listen to the shout] at YouTube).
{{DEFAULTSORT:Go for the Eyes!}} [[Category:References to video games]] [[Category:Skills that affect allies]]
[[de:"Zielt auf die Augen!"]]

