'''[[Hero skill trainer]]s''' *[[Hoju]] (Gate of Torment)
==Notes== *The health gain occurs after damage on skill activation from skills like [[Spiteful Spirit]] or [[Environment Effect]]s like [[Dreadful Pain]].
==Trivia== *The [[skill icon]] resembles that of the skill [["Go for the Eyes!"]]. Also, the two figures below the paragon in the icon are necromancers wearing [[Necromancer Sunspear armor|Sunspear armor]], the same figure shown in [["Never Surrender!"]].
[[Category:Skills offered by hero skill trainers]] {{DEFAULTSORT:Help Me!}}
