{{Skill infobox | name = "I Am Unstoppable!" | id = 2356 | campaign = Eye of the North | attribute = Norn rank | type = Shout | energy = 5 | recharge = 30 | pve-only = y | causes1 = Increased Armor Rating | causes2 = Knockdown Immunity | causes3 = Condition Immunity | description = [[Shout]]. For {{gr2|16|20}} seconds, you have +24 [[Armor rating|armor]] and cannot be [[knocked down]] or [[Crippled]]. | concise description = Shout. ({{gr2|16|20}} seconds.) You have +24 armor and cannot be knocked-down or Crippled. | aoe = None | removes1 = Condition }}
{{Skill progression max10 |title track = [[Norn rank]] |var1 name = [[Duration]] |var1 at0 = 16 |var1 at10 = 20 }}
==Acquisition== '''[[Skill quest]]s''' *[[Cold as Ice]] ([[Sifhalla]])
==Related skills== * {{skill icon|Balanced Stance}} * {{skill icon|Dolyak Signet}} * {{skill icon|Illusion of Haste}}
== Notes == * This skill will remove existing Crippled when used, although this is not stated in its description. This is similar to other [[Skill quick reference#Skills that provide immunity to a condition|skills that provide immunity to a condition]], except for [[Frigid Armor]].
{{bug|Similarly to [[Illusionary Weaponry]] and [[Mantra of Signets]], the armor provided by this skill is only applied at the end of the [[armor calculation]]. As such, it is not counted in the [[effect stacking#Effect caps|bonus armor cap]] of +25 and is not reduced by [[Armor penetration]].}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:I am unstoppable!}}

