__NOTOC__ {{Skill infobox | id = 333 | name = "I Will Avenge You!" | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Warrior | attribute = Strength | type = Shout | energy = 5 | recharge = 45 | target = self | range = compass | aoe = none | causes1 = Health Regeneration | causes2 = Increased Attack Speed | description = [[Shout]]. For each [[Corpse|dead]] [[ally]], you gain 10 seconds of +{{gr|3|7}} [[Health regeneration]] and your [[attack speed]] increases by 25%. | concise description = Shout. You have +{{gr|3|7}} Health regeneration and attack 25% faster (10 seconds for each dead ally). }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Strength]] | var1 name = [[Health regeneration]] | var1 at0 = 3 | var1 at15 = 7}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Captain Greywind]] ([[North Kryta Province]]) * [[Master Scout Kiera]] ([[Henge of Denravi]]) * [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]])
== Notes == * This skill is often referred to by its initials, "IWAY". * All dead allies on your [[compass]] count for this skill. ** Because of this, this skill can be maintained indefinitely on certain missions (such as [[Dzagonur Bastion]]) if enough allied pets within the party are killed. * Non-stop upkeep of this skill's effect requires 5 dead allies, 3 if under the effects of [[Enduring Harmony]]. * Without a dead ally, the shout will still appear in a speech bubble as usual but no effect at all seems to be applied. [[Echo]]es will not trigger. * When used by a [[Player versus Environment|PvE]] [[foe]], this skill will consider all dead PvE foes in compass range as allies of the PvE foe using this skill, even foes of different [[creature type]]s.<!--Tested with [[White Mantle Justiciar]] in The Black Curtain during The False Gods with dead Spined Aloes and Bog Skale Blighters in compass range, but no dead humans.-->
== Trivia == * A [[PvP]] team [[build]] based on this skill started the [[-way]] suffixes in [[metagame]].
== See also == * [["I Will Avenge You" Warriors]] {{DEFAULTSORT:I Will Avenge You!}}

