{{Skill infobox | id = 3162‎ | name = "There's not enough time!!" | special = Monster | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Monster | type = Shout | energy = 10 | recharge = 20 | aoe = earshot | causes1 = Increased Attack Speed | causes2 = Increased Movement Speed | causes3 = Decreased Activation Time | description = [[Shout]]. For 20 seconds, all [[creature]]s within [[earshot]] [[Attack speed|attack]], [[Speed boost|move]], and [[Activation time|activate]] [[skills]] 100% faster. | concise description = Shout. (20 seconds.) Creatures in earshot attack, move, and activate skills 100% faster. }}
