==Notes==
*This skill is used by Afflicted in [[Factions]], but not in [[Winds of Change]].
*[[Boss]]es will deal double damage.
*This skill's type is not specified in its description.
*[[Blood Bond]] can be used to regain some of the health lost to this skill's damage.
* Use caution with [[area of effect]] skills, since killing multiple Afflicted at once will cause a massive [[spike]].

