{{Skill infobox | id = 2416 | name = Air of Superiority | campaign = Eye of the North | attribute = Asura rank | pve-only = y | type = Skill | energy = 5 | recharge = 20 | causes1 = Healing | causes2 = Energy Gain | causes3 = Recharge | removes1 = Condition | description=[[Skill (skill type)|Skill]]. For {{gr2|20|30}} seconds you gain a random Asura benefit every time you earn [[experience]] from killing an enemy. | concise description = Skill. ({{gr2|20|30}} seconds). Gain a random Asura benefit every time you earn experience from killing an enemy. }}
{{Skill progression max10 |title track = [[Asura rank]] |var1 name = [[Duration]] |var1 at0 = 20 |var1 at10 = 30}}
==Acquisition== '''[[Skill quest]]s''' *[[The Path to Revelations]] ([[Tarnished Haven]])
== Notes == * This skill only activates if you receive at least 1 XP from a foe death. * The benefits gained can be identified by the dialogue bubbles above the character's head: ::{| {{STDT|#6A3}} |- align="center" valign="top" |- style="background:#ADA;" ! Boast !! Benefit || Activation chance (%) |- align="center" | ''"Buwahahaha!"'' || All [[condition]]s removed from self || 30% |- align="center" | ''"Kneel Before Your Master!"'' || Double XP gained || 20% |- align="center" | ''"Knowledge is Power!"'' || [[Heal]]ed for 50 [[health]] || 20% |- align="center" | ''"You're No Match for My Brains!"'' || Gain 5 [[energy]] || 20% |- align="center" | ''"Is There Anything I Can't Do?"'' || [[Recharge]] all skills || 10% |}
* Skills that require a [[morale boost]], such as [[Resurrection Signet]], [[Sunspear Rebirth Signet]], and [[Celestial skill]]s, are '''not''' recharged by ''"Is There Anything I Can't Do?"''. * Experience [[scroll]]s stack with ''"Kneel Before Your Master"''.
{{anomaly|Unlike other skills without an activation time, this skill has the standard [[aftercast delay]] of {{3/4}} second and cannot be used while moving or activating another skill.}}
== Trivia == * The boast ''"You're No Match for My Brains!"'' is a quote from the movie ''[[w:The Princess Bride|The Princess Bride]]''. * The phrase ''"Knowledge is Power!"'' was coined by [[w:Francis Bacon|Francis Bacon]] and subsequently became a pop-culture reference due to [[w:Schoolhouse Rock|Schoolhouse Rock]] and various [[w:Public service announcement|PSAs]] in the 80s and 90s which borrowed the term. * The phrase ''"Kneel Before Your Master!"'' is a quote from ''[[w:Masters of the Universe (film)|Masters of the Universe]]''. * This skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[{{PAGENAME}}/Skill history|skill history]] for details.
