== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Angelic Protection}}
== Notes == * Innate bonus on the [[Guild Lord]] * Effect: Limits the amount of damage he can take per second. If the Guild Lord loses health due to damage-over-time effects or other direct loss of health, then once every second, it heals him for the amount of health he lost that exceeds the limit. * The limits range from 25 [[damage per second]] at the start of the match to 300 damage per second.

