==Acquisition== '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' *[[Baram]] ([[The Kodash Bazaar]]) *[[Resh]] ([[Yahnur Market]]) *[[Zendeht]] ([[Gate of Torment]]) '''[[Hero skill trainer]]s''' *[[Warden of Whispers (The Kodash Bazaar)|Warden of Whispers]] (The Kodash Bazaar)
== Related skills == *{{skill icon|Spirit Bond}}
==Notes== *This skill mimics the effect of the [[Guild Lord]]'s [[Amulet of Protection]]. *Under Angelic Protection, you take the damage first and then are healed. If you take more damage than you have [[health]] remaining, you will die. *Unlike [[Protective Spirit]], this skill will protect even against small damage [[packet]]s if there are enough of them. An example would be the large mobs of [[Avicara Fierce]] in [[Mineral Springs]] who use [[Ignite Arrows]] and [[Dual Shot]]. {{anomaly|Unlike most typeless skills with no [[activation time]], this skill cannot be activated in the middle of another [[action]] and has a slight [[aftercast delay]].}}
