__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 83 | name = Animate Bone Horror | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Necromancer | attribute = Death Magic | type = Spell | energy = 10 | activation = 3 | recharge = 5 | target = self | range = Casting | aoe = none | causes1 = Exploits Corpse | causes2 = Minion | requires1 = Corpse | description = [[Spell]]. Exploit nearest [[corpse]] to animate a [[level]] {{gr|1|17}} [[Bone Horror|bone horror]]. | concise description = Spell. Creates a level {{gr|1|17}} bone horror. {{grey|Exploits a fresh corpse.}} }}
{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Death Magic]] |var1 name = [[Level]] |var1 at0 = 1 |var1 at15 = 17}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]s''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[The Necromancer's Novice]] ([[The Catacombs]] - [[Ascalon (pre-Searing)|pre-Searing]]) ** [[The Stolen Artifact]] ([[Sardelac Sanitarium]]) '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * Prophecies ** [[Halbrik]] ([[Ascalon City (outpost)|Ascalon City]] - pre-Searing) ** [[Sir Bertran]] ([[Ascalon City]]) ** [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]]) '''[[Profession changer]]s''' * Prophecies ** [[Zratha Kor]] ([[Heroes' Audience]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Animate Bone Minions}} * {{skill icon|Aura of the Lich}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|Malign Intervention}}
== Notes == * Bone Horrors are [[melee attack]]ers, and as such are very useful for blocking choke points, or preventing/slowing enemy movement. * Like all minions, they are very susceptible to [[AoE]] damage.
== See also == * [[List of minion skills]]
