{{Skill infobox | id = 85 | name = Animate Bone Minions | campaign = Core | profession = Necromancer | attribute = Death Magic | type = Spell | energy = 15 | recharge = 5 | activation = 3 | target = self | range = Casting | aoe = none | causes1 = Exploits Corpse | causes2 = Minion | requires1 = Corpse | description = [[Spell]]. Exploit nearest [[corpse]] to animate two level {{gr|0|12}} [[bone minion]]s. | concise description = Spell. Creates two level {{gr|0|12}} bone minions. {{gray|Exploits a fresh corpse.}} }}
{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Death Magic]] |var1 name = Level |var1 at0 = 0 |var1 at15 = 12}}
{{TOCright}} == Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]s''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[The Royal Papers]] ([[Fishermen's Haven]]) * [[Factions]] ** [[Skill Chaining]] ([[Shing Jea Monastery]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Primary Training]] ([[Churrhir Fields]]) ** [[Choose Your Secondary Profession (Nightfall quest)|Choose Your Secondary Profession]] (Churrhir Fields) '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * Prophecies ** [[Bartoch]] ([[Droknar's Forge]]) ** [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]]) * Factions ** [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]]) * Nightfall ** [[Tohn]] ([[Kamadan, Jewel of Istan]]) '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * Prophecies ** [[Bakkir the Forsaken]] ([[Gates of Kryta]]) ** [[Bane Darkfist]] ([[D'Alessio Seaboard]]) ** [[Amir the Overripe]] ([[Nebo Terrace]]) ** [[Zukra Cadava]] ([[Divinity Coast]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Animate Bone Horror}} * {{skill icon|Aura of the Lich}} ([[elite]])
== Notes == * Bone Minions are useful with skill combinations that rely on the minions dying, such as [[Jagged Bones]], [[Death Nova]] or cause them to die, such as [[Putrid Flesh]] or [[Feast for the Dead]]. It is generally useful with [[build]]s that rely on [[Soul Reaping]] for [[energy management]]. * This spell will trigger [[Explosive Growth]], [[Boon of Creation]], and [[Spirit's Gift]] twice.
== Trivia == * The creature in the [[skill icon]] appears similar to a [[Scarab]].
