__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 75 | name = Arcane Echo | campaign = Core | profession = Mesmer | type = Enchantment Spell | energy = 15 | recharge = 20 | activation = 2 | causes1 = Skill Copying | description = [[Enchantment Spell]]. If you cast a [[spell]] in the next 20 seconds, Arcane Echo is replaced with that spell for 20 seconds. Arcane Echo ends prematurely if you use a non-spell skill. | concise description = Enchantment Spell. (20 seconds.) Arcane Echo becomes the next spell you use (20 seconds). {{gray|This enchantment ends if you use any skill that is not a spell.}} }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[Ephaz]] ([[Beetletun]]) ** [[Master Scout Kiera]] ([[Henge of Denravi]]) ** [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]]) * [[Factions]] ** [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]]) ** [[Akane]] ([[Senji's Corner]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Kenohir]] ([[Command Post]]) ** [[Iasha]] ([[Wehhan Terraces]]) '''[[Hero skill trainer]]s''' * Nightfall ** [[Warden of Whispers (The Kodash Bazaar)|Warden of Whispers]] ([[The Kodash Bazaar]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Echo}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|Rollerbeetle Echo}}
== Notes == * Combine Echo and Arcane Echo to create [[echo chain]]s, allowing you to use three copies of any single skill. * If the next skill after Arcane Echo is not a spell, this enchantment will end with no effect. * Arcane Echo will only recharge normally if no spell was copied. If a spell was copied, the copy remains for 20 seconds, after which Arcane Echo is [[disable]]d for 20 seconds. ** Consider using [[Auspicious Incantation]] before Arcane Echo for [[energy management]], since the [[recharge time]] will not be increased. * If used to copy a [[Skill quick reference#Skills that are replaced with other skills|spell that can copy another skill or spell]], the copy [[duration]] of that spell is used and will bypass Arcane Echo's 20-second copy duration. ** E.g., if used to copy Echo, whatever skill that is copied by the Arcane Echo version of Echo will remain as that skill for 30 seconds and then revert back to Arcane Echo. {{anomaly|Arcane Echo's description omits the fact that it cannot copy itself.}} {{Outdated info|}} ;[[Feedback:Game updates/20190205|February 05, 2019 update]]; please verify changes to [[Hero behavior|AI behavior]].
== Trivia == * The three purple circles around the figure in the [[skill icon]] resemble this skill's casting animation.
