{{Skill infobox | id = 1085 | name = Ash Blast | campaign = Factions | profession = Elementalist | attribute = Earth Magic | type = Hex spell | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 15 | causes1 = Earth Damage | causes2 = Miss | description = [[Hex Spell]]. [[Target]] and [[adjacent]] [[foe]]s are struck for {{gr|35|65}} [[earth damage]]. [[Burning]] foes struck by Ash Blast are hexed for 5 seconds and have a {{gr|20|75}}% chance to [[miss]] with [[attack]]s. | concise description = Hex Spell. Deals {{gr|35|65}} earth damage. Burning foes are hexed for 5 seconds and miss {{gr|20|75}}% of attacks. Also strikes adjacent. | aoe = adjacent }}
