__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 2415 | name = Asuran Scan | campaign = Eye of the North | profession = | attribute = Asura rank | pve-only = y | type = Hex Spell | energy = 5 | recharge = 5 | targert = foes | range = Casting | aoe = none | causes1 = Unblockable | prevents1 = Miss | prevents2 = Block | removes1 = Death Penalty | description = [[Hex spell|Hex Spell]]. For {{gr2|9|12}} seconds your [[attack]]s cannot [[miss]] [[target]] [[foe]]. [[Death|Killing]] a foe hexed with Asuran Scan removes 5% [[Death Penalty]]. | concise description = Hex Spell. ({{gr2|9|12}} seconds.) You cannot miss target foe. If you kill this foe, you lose 5% Death Penalty. }}
{{Skill progression max10 |title track = [[Asura rank]] |var1 name = [[Duration]] |var1 at0 = 9 |var1 at10 = 12 }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]s''' * [[The Cipher of Grenth]] ([[Tarnished Haven]])
== Related skills == *{{skill icon|Expose Defenses}} *{{skill icon|Rigor Mortis}}
== Notes == * The caster receives the Death Penalty (DP) reduction when the target foe dies, regardless of who delivered the killing blow. * The DP is removed before applying any [[Morale Boost]]s; starting with a DP of 5% or less, you end up with a 2% boost after killing a [[boss]]. * This hex only applies to attacks that would otherwise miss or be [[block]]ed; it does not prevent hits from [[Line of sight|straying, being obstructed, or being dodged]]. It also does not prevent [[fail]]ure due to unmet attribute requirements, e.g. [[Oath Shot]] will still fail 50% of the time if [[Expertise]] is below 8. * This is the only hex without a specified [[activation time]]. It casts instantly, but it has an [[aftercast delay]] and cannot be used in mid-[[action]].
{{Bug|Foes affected by this skill cannot miss.}}
{{Bug|While target foe is hexed, you cannot miss other foes.}}
{{anomaly|This hex also prevents the target from [[block]]ing your attacks.}}
== Trivia == * The functionality of this skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[/Skill history|skill history]] for details. * This is the only skill (outside of [[Spirit Form (disguise)|the Underworld]]) that removes Death Penalty.

