== Notes == * The fastest way to capture this skill is to start the Raisu Palace mission, as Sword Ancient Kai is near the beginning of the mission. * This is one of the few Factions elite skills that are obtainable in Nightfall; however, if you do not own Factions, you won't be able to capture it. * This is one of the skills with the lowest adrenal cost, the others being the monster skills, [[Jadoth's Storm of Judgment]] and [[Ehzah from Above]]. * The adrenaline is also gained on renew.
