== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[Markis]] ([[Iron Mines of Moladune]]) ** [[Snyk the Hundred Tongue]] ([[Abaddon's Mouth]]) ** [[Cairn the Cunning]] ([[Riverside Province (explorable area)]], only during the [[War in Kryta]]) * [[Factions]] ** [[Aurora]] ([[Boreas Seabed]]) ** [[Chkkr Thousand Tail]] ([[Drazach Thicket]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Commander Kubeh]] ([[Arkjok Ward]], only during [[The Great Escape]]) ** [[Bearer of Misfortune]] ([[Domain of Pain]]) * [[Eye of the North]] ** [[Groknar Weazlewortz]] ([[Against the Charr]]) ** [[Docu Kindleshot]] ([[Blood Washes Blood]]) ** [[Frostmaw Spawn]] ([[Frostmaw's Burrow]]) ** [[Storm of Destruction]] ([[Riven Earth]])
