{{Skill infobox | id = 350 | name = Belly Smash | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Warrior | attribute = Hammer Mastery | type = Hammer Attack | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 10 | causes1 = Blind | description = [[Hammer Attack]]. If this [[attack]] strikes a [[foe]] who is [[Knock down|knocked down]], the resulting dust cloud will [[blind]] [[adjacent]] foes for {{gr|3|7}} seconds. | concise description = Hammer Attack. Inflicts Blindness condition to adjacent foes ({{gr|3|7}} seconds) if target foe is knocked down. | aoe = adjacent | target = untargeted | pbaoe = self }}
