__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 823 | name = Burning Speed | campaign = Factions | profession = Elementalist | attribute = Fire Magic | type = Enchantment Spell | energy = 10 | activation = {{1/4}} | aoe = adjacent | target = untargeted | pbaoe = self | causes1 = Burning | causes2 = Increased Movement Speed | description = [[Enchantment Spell]]. For 7 seconds, you are set [[Burning|on fire]] and [[Speed boost|move {{gr|30|45}}% faster]]. When Burning Speed [[End effect|ends]], all [[adjacent]] [[foe]]s are set on fire for {{gr|3|9}} seconds. | concise description = Enchantment Spell. (7 seconds.) You move {{gr|30|45}}% faster. {{gray|You suffer from Burning (7 seconds).}} End effect: inflicts Burning condition ({{gr|3|9}} seconds) on adjacent foes. }}
