{{Skill infobox | id = 1044 | name = Dark Prison | campaign = Factions | profession = Assassin | attribute = Deadly Arts | type = Hex Spell | energy = 10 | activation = {{1/4}} | recharge = 30 | causes1 = Shadow Step | causes2 = Decreased Movement Speed | description = [[Hex Spell]]. [[Shadow Step]] to [[target]] [[foe]]. For {{gr|1|6}} seconds, that foe [[Snare (tactic)|moves 33% slower]]. | concise description = Hex Spell. Shadow Step to target foe. This foe moves 33% slower ({{gr|1|6}} seconds). }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Deadly Arts]] | var1 name = [[Duration]] | var1 at0 = 1 | var1 at15 = 6}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]]) * [[Akane]] ([[Senji's Corner]]) * [[Ziinyingmao Kaga]] ([[Dragon's Throat (outpost)|Dragon's Throat]]) '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Tahkayun Tsi]] ([[Kinya Province]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Shadow Prison}} ([[elite]])
== Notes == * The shadow step and the hex are considered separate effects: **If the shadow step fails (i.e. if the target is in an inaccessible location), the target will still suffer the movement speed hex. **If the hex fails (i.e. the target is under the effects of [[Hex Breaker]]), you will still shadow step to the target.

