{{Skill infobox | name = Earth Shattering Blow | profession = Monster | special = Monster | type = Attack | campaign = Nightfall | description = [[Attack]]. All [[foe]]s [[in the area]] of [[target]] take 100 [[blunt damage]] and are [[knock down|knocked down]]. Surrounding foes take 80 [[earth damage]]. | concise description = Attack. Deals 100 blunt damage and causes knock-down to foes in the area of target. 80 earth damage to surrounding foes.}}
==Notes== *This monster skill is only used by the fallen god [[Abaddon]]. *Abaddon will use this skill only while not chained and will only hit locations associated to an unchained hand. *This skill will randomly hit one of the four paths near the central crossing even if no [[party]] members are standing there. Abaddon will use his right hand to hit the south and the west and his left to hit the north and the east path.
