{{skill infobox | id = 2372 | name = Edification | campaign = Eye of the North | attribute = Asura rank | type = Title | description = [[Title (skill type)|Title]]. You have +{{gr2|5|15}} maximum [[Energy]] in Asura territory. | concise description = Title. You have +{{gr2|5|15}} maximum Energy in Asura territory. }} {{Skill progression max10 |title track = Asura rank |var1 name = + Maximum energy |var1 at0 = 5 |var1 at10 = 15 }}
==Acquisition== *Talk to [[Lexx]] [Asuran Talent Scout] in [[Rata Sum]] after attaining the first rank of the [[Asura rank|Asura title track]].
== Notes == * This cannot be equipped on the [[skill bar]]. While a [[character]] displays the Asura title, this effect is applied to that character and all of their [[hero]]es. * ''Asura territory'' includes all towns, outposts, and explorable areas in the [[Tarnished Coast]], as well as [[Gadd's Encampment]] and [[Sparkfly Swamp]]. ** Edification also provides extra energy during all [[Finding the Bloodstone]] and [[The Elusive Golemancer]] instances. * Hero energy remains the same in outposts whether the title is switched on or off.

