==Trivia== *This is a reference to ''Falcon Punch'', a trademark attack of [[wikipedia:Captain Falcon|Captain Falcon]], who is found in both the anime [[wikipedia:F-Zero: GP Legend (anime)|F-Zero: GP Legend]] and the [[wikipedia:F-Zero|F-Zero]] video game series. This refers directly to the Super Smash Bros. series, in which Captain Falcon is a playable character and Falcon Punch is one of his special attacks with a fiery animation.
