== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Contagion}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|Epidemic}} * {{skill icon|Extend Conditions}} (elite)
== Notes == * Only triggers on new conditions; re-applying an existing condition will not trigger the hex. * When the hex is applied, if the target has at least one condition, Dazed is applied. For the duration, whenever the target acquires a new condition, if it had at least another condition, the Dazed is (re) applied. * Fevered Dreams will spread the Dazed it applies. * Works well with shouts inflicting conditions, most notably [["You Move Like a Dwarf!"]], [["You Are All Weaklings!"]], and [["Finish Him!"]]. {{Bug|If target foe is suffering from at least one condition when this hex is cast, Dazed will be applied.}} {{Bug|The Dazed is spread again when renewed.}}
