__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | name = Frenzied Defense | id = 1700 | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Warrior | type = Stance | energy = 5 | recharge = 10 | causes1 = Block | description = [[Stance]]. For 8 seconds, you have a 75% chance to [[block]] incoming [[attack]]s, but take double [[damage]]. | concise description = Stance. (8 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. {{gray|You take double damage.}} }}
