==Notes== *Can be effectively used by secondary warriors, since it is the only [[No Attribute skill]] that provides blocking. *[[Damage reduction]], such as [[Protective Spirit]], will be taken into account after Frenzied Defense, therefore mitigating the double damage. **If not using skills such as Protective Spirit, consider using a [[cancel stance]]. *Used with [[Spirit Bond]], the attacks that are not blocked are more likely to trigger the healing effect and can effectively negate all incoming damage from attacks.
