== Notes == * Generally used by [[sword]] and [[axe]] warriors in [[PvP]]. [[Hammer]] warriors tend to use [[Flail]] instead, partly due to their lower [[armor rating]] and partly because Flail has less of a drawback when foes are [[Knock down|knocked down]]. * [[Damage reduction]], such as [[Protective Spirit]], will be taken into account after Frenzy, therefore mitigating the double damage. ** If not using skills such as Protective Spirit, the use of a [[cancel stance]], such as [[Rush]], is advisable. * Frenzy is generally too risky to use on secondary warriors, as their lower armor rating combined with the Frenzy drawback makes them too vulnerable. * It is the only stance available in pre-Searing.
