{{otheruses|the Monster skill|the temporarily available [[Bonus Mission Pack]] skill|Giant Stomp (Turai Ossa)}} {{Skill infobox | id = 530 | name = Giant Stomp | campaign = Core | profession = Monster | special = Monster | type = Attack | energy = 10 | activation = 4 | recharge = 32 | target = self | description = [[Attack]]. All [[foe]]s [[earshot|within range]] are [[Knock down|knocked down]] and take 25 [[damage]]. | concise description = Attack. Causes knock-down and deals 25 damage to foes in range. | aoe = earshot }}
== Related skills == * {{monster skill icon|Agnar's Rage}} * {{monster skill icon|Tremor}} * {{monster skill icon|Giant Stomp (Turai Ossa)}}
== Notes ==
* Giant Stomp activates halfway through its stated [[activation time]], i.e. after 2 seconds. * Most foes that use Giant Stomp carry the [[passive]] skill [[Stun Immunity]], that prevents them from stunning each other. ** [[Sadistic Giant|Sadistic]] and [[Nomad Giant]]s are not knocked down by this skill, even though they do not carry Stun Immunity. ** [[Earthbind]] will bypass the immunity, as it also affects enemy knockdown skills. * The skill deals [[armor-ignoring damage|armor-ignoring]] [[physical damage]]. Consequently, it is affected by physical [[damage reduction]], such as [[Rune of Absorption]]. * This skill will also knock down [[miniature]]s.
; Creatures using the skill * [[Giant]]s (all types) * [[Jotun Skullsmasher]] * [[Summit Beastmaster]] * [[Summit Giant Herder]]
{{anomaly|Giant Stomp does not act as an [[attack]], despite its classification: the damage cannot be [[block]]ed and doesn't trigger skills like [[Empathy]].}}
{{anomaly|Contrary to the descriptions, Giant Stomp damages and knocks down ''all'' [[creature]]s (excluding the user) within [[earshot]] of the user, whether [[ally]], foe or [[Foe#Passive foe|passive]] [[charmable animal]].}}
