__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 1096 | name = Glyph of Essence | campaign = Factions | profession = Elementalist | type = Glyph | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 20 | causes1 = Decreased Activation Time | causes2 = Energy Loss | description = [[Glyph]]. For 15 seconds, your next [[spell]] [[Activation time|casts]] instantly but causes you to lose all [[Energy]]. | concise description = Glyph. (15 seconds.) Your next spell casts instantly. {{gray|You lose all Energy.}} }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]])
== Related skills == * {{Skill icon|Glyph of Sacrifice}}
== Notes == * The amount of energy loss can be lowered by [[energy hiding]]. * Energy gain skills such as [[Auspicious Incantation]] or [[Attunement]]s will not help to counter the energy loss, as it happens after the gain from these skills, leaving you at 0 energy. * Synergizes well with [[Ether Lord]], since the energy loss would happen anyway. Synergizes even better with [[Rebirth]], since it has an especially long cast time.
== Trivia == * The functionality of this skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[/Skill history|skill revision history]] for details.

{{Skill infobox | name = Glyph of Immolation | id = 2060 | campaign = Eye of the North | profession = Elementalist | attribute = Fire Magic | type = Glyph | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 10 | causes1 = Burning | description = [[Glyph]]. For 15 seconds, your next {{gr|1|4}} [[spell]][s] that [[target]][s] a [[foe]] also cause[s] [[Burning]] for {{gr|1|4}} second[s]. | concise description = Glyph. (15 seconds.) Your next {{gr|1|4}} spell[s] that target[s] a foe also inflict[s] Burning condition ({{gr|1|4}} second[s]). }}
{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Fire Magic]] |var1 name = [[Spell]]s affected |var1 at0 = 1 |var1 at15 = 4 |var2 name = [[Burning]] [[duration]] |var2 at0 = 1 |var2 at15 = 4}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Micah Fergson]] ([[Eye of the North (outpost)|Eye of the North]]) * [[Sida]] ([[Gunnar's Hold]]) * [[Ybbob]] ([[Rata Sum]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Double Dragon}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|Elemental Flame}} * {{skill icon|Signet of Suffering}} (elite)
== Notes == * Burning is applied ''before'' the effect of the spell, thus the glyph combines well with skills that require a condition (e.g. [[Virulence]] or [[Vile Miasma]]) or burning (e.g. [[Glowing Gaze]] or [[Searing Flames]]). * This skill only burns the targeted foe, even if the spell has an [[area of effect]] (e.g. [[Fireball]]); it does not have any effect on [[PBAoE|point blank area-of-effect]] spells (e.g. [[Inferno]]). * When used with [[projectile spell]]s, the burning takes effect after activation, but before the projectile starts to move; the target will burn even if the projectile misses.

