== Related skills == * {{skill icon|"Charge!"}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|"Fall Back!"}} * {{Skill icon|"Incoming!"}} (elite) * {{Skill icon|"Retreat!"}}
==Notes== *This skill will remain on an ally even if all enchantments end or are removed, but the speed boost will be lost until another enchantment is applied. *This skill increases average speed by '''<font color=green>4.17...14.17...16.67%</font>''' if used every time it recharges and ally/allies is/are enchanted for the full duration of Godspeed. * If the team members do not already use their own enchantments, one can use the following options to enchant and get the speed boost on as many of them as possible: ** Party wide enchantments spells: [[Aegis]], [[Dwayna's Sorrow]], [[Magnetic Surge]], [[Swirling Aura]], [[Magnetic Aura]] (all three if overcast) and [[order]] spells. *** [[Dwayna's Sorrow]] is the only one to combine both perfect upkeep and long lasting duration. It is also notably cheap with a short casting time. ** [[Spam]]mable long-lasting enchantments: [[Tainted Flesh]] or [[Vigorous Spirit]] mostly. ** [[Upkeep|Maintained enchantment]]s. {{anomaly|This skill doesn't have punctuation in its name like other shouts, even though the character still shouts it with the punctuation.}}
