__NOTOC__{{otheruses|the elite skill|the unique scythe of the same name|Grenth's Grasp (scythe)}} {{Skill infobox | id = 1756 | name = Grenth's Grasp | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Dervish | attribute = Wind Prayers | type = Flash Enchantment Spell | elite = y | energy = 5 | recharge = 10 | causes1 = Crippled | causes2 = Condition | removes1 = Condition | description = [[Elite]] [[Flash Enchantment Spell]]. For 20 seconds, if you are wielding a [[Icy|cold]] [[weapon]], your [[attack skill]]s also [[Crippled|Cripple]] that {{sic}} [[foe]] for {{gr|1|11}} second[s] and you transfer 1 [[condition]] from yourself to that foe. | concise description = Elite Flash Enchantment Spell. (20 seconds.) Inflicts Crippled condition ({{gr|1|11}} second[s]) with your attack skills and transfer 1 condition. {{gray|No effect unless wielding a cold weapon.}} }}
