== Notes == * Rather than causing the hex cast to fail as the description states, this skill prevents the hex from being applied to the user. ** Initial effects, such as [[Dark Prison]]'s [[Shadow Step]], ''will'' still take place. ** AoE hexes like [[Rust]] ''will'' still apply normally to all other targets. ** End effects from hexes like [[Shatterstone]] will ''not'' trigger.
== Trivia == * This skill was called "Mantra of Hex Shattering" during beta testing. [[Category:Mesmer skill rewards]] [[Category:Skills offered by hero skill trainers]]

