== Notes == * This skill will cause maximum health degeneration at rank 14 and above. * The healing effect scales to be ~50% of the hex's maximum damage potential. For example, at rank 12, the skill will inflict a maximum of 216 damage, healing 113 points when it ends. * You can increase the [[duration]] of the hex, increasing the net damage without affecting the amount of healing: ** Using [[Mantra of Persistence]]. ** By re-applying the hex before it runs out. * Removing the hex early (e.g. via [[Cure Hex]]) will trigger the healing. Use a [[cover]] hex to prevent this. * The healing caused by Illusion of Pain does not trigger [[Scourge Healing]]. * The [[AI]] only uses this skill on targets whose health is below two thirds of maximum.
