== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Thengen]] ([[Port Sledge]]) * [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]])
== Notes == * Combines well with [[Foul Feast]], [[Cautery Signet]] and [[Martyr]]. * Combines well with [[Cultist's Fervor]] and [[Signet of Suffering]]. * You do not ''gain'' conditions, but you do ''lose'' them. Thus you trigger [[Fragility]] only once, and do not trigger abilities like [[Contagion]]. * This skill is the only way to prevent [[Dazed]] and the interrupt from its application. This is also the only way for a player to become immune to [[Poison]], [[Deep Wound]], [[Weakness]], [[Bleeding]] and [[Cracked Armor]]. {{bug|This skill ''does'' transfer [[Bleeding]], [[Disease]], and [[Poison]] to [[minion]]s, despite them being non-[[fleshy]].}}
