__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | name = Jagged Bones | id = 1355 | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Necromancer | attribute = Death Magic | type = Enchantment Spell | elite = y | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 15 | target = minions | range = Casting | aoe = none | causes1 = Minion | causes2 = Bleeding | removes1 = | requires1 = Minion | description = [[Elite]] [[Enchantment Spell]]. For 30 seconds, whenever [[target]] [[minion|undead servant]] [[Death|dies]], it is replaced by a [[level]] {{gr|0|15}} [[Jagged Horror|jagged horror]] that causes [[Bleeding]] with each of its [[attack]]s. | concise description = Elite Enchantment Spell. (30 seconds.) When target undead servant dies, it is replaced by a level {{gr|0|15}} jagged horror that inflicts Bleeding with attacks. }}
{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Death Magic]] |var1 name = [[Level]] |var1 at0 = 0 |var1 at15 = 15 }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Master of Misery]] ([[Depths of Madness]]) ** [[Shadow of Fear (boss)]] ([[Nightfallen Jahai]], only during [[Breaking the Broken]]) ** [[Emissary of Dhuum (necromancer)|Emissary of Dhuum]] (Nightfallen Jahai, only during [[Dark Gateway]]) * [[Eye of the North]] ** [[Avarr the Fallen]] ([[Jaga Moraine]]) ** [[Taskmaster Bellok]] ([[Vloxen Excavations]], level 2) ** [[Taskmaster Nard]] ([[Battledepths]], only during [[Attack on Jalis's Camp]]) ** [[The Master]] ([[Cathedral of Flames]], level 2)
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Animate Shambling Horror}} * {{skill icon|Malign Intervention}}
== Notes == * The effects of this spell occur when a minion dies. Thus, [[Shambling Horror]]s will produce two Jagged Horrors on death in total, [[Flesh Golem]]s will still leave an exploitable corpse, [[Bone Minion]]s can be used to create Jagged Horrors of a higher level than they were and finally, Jagged Horrors created by this skill may be recycled endlessly. * The created Jagged Horror is bound to the previous minion's controller, not to the Jagged Bones' user. ** Jagged Horrors created by this enchantment will trigger [[Explosive Growth]], [[Boon of Creation]] and [[Spirit's Gift]] if the previous minion's controller had one of those enchantments active. ** Minions created benefit from the controllers [[Spawning Power]]. * Unless a minion is targeted, Jagged Bones will be cast on a random minion that is not already enchanted with Jagged Bones. * The bleeding lasts for 25 seconds. * Jagged Bones has the shortest cast time of any skill that creates an allied minion. {{anomaly|The descriptions do not mention the [[duration]] of the bleeding inflicted by the Jagged Horror.}}
