{{Skill infobox | id = 535 | name = Jagged Crystal Skin | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Monster | special = Monster | type = Stance | energy = 5 | recharge = 10 | description = [[Stance]]. (monster only) For 10 seconds, whenever you are hit by [[physical damage]], [[nearby]] [[foe]]s take 100 [[damage]]. | concise description = Stance. (monster only) (10 seconds.) 100 damage to foes near you whenever you take physical damage. | aoe = nearby }}
== Notes == * This skill is used by the dragon [[Glint]] in [[The Dragon's Lair]]. * Because this skill can quickly devastate [[melee attack]]ers, it is highly recommended to bring a [[Stance#Skills_countering_stances|stance removal skill]] or non-physical type ([[icy]]/[[fiery]]/[[shocking]]/[[ebon]]) weapons when facing Glint. * [[Greater Conflagration]], [[Judge's Insight]], and many [[Dervish]] skills are also useful as they convert physical damage to other [[damage type]]s, thus bypassing the effect of Jagged Crystal Skin.
[[de:Raue Kristallhaut]]

