== Notes == * There is a 3 second delay between dropping the ashes and resurrection. * If you are holding this when you die, you drop it and are resurrected. * Your team will [[wipe]] in PvE and still lose an [[annihilation]] round even if your last remaining party member is holding the ashes after being killed. * This skill cannot be cast while under effect of [[Frozen Soil]]. The ashes, however, will successfully resurrect party members if dropped while in range of a Frozen Soil spirit. ** Combine with Frozen Soil to prevent enemy resurrection while enabling it for your own party. * This skill has a distinctive caster aura at the end of casting and a distinctive urn graphic.
