{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Inspiration Magic]] |var1 name = [[Energy]] gain |var1 at0 = 10 |var1 at15 = 25}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[Facet of Chaos]] ([[The Dragon's Lair]]) ** [[Featherclaw]] ([[Snake Dance]]) * [[Eye of the North]] ** [[Facet of Illusions]] ([[Magus Stones]] during [[The Cipher of Lyssa]] and [[Varajar Fells]] during [[The Path to Revelations]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Energy Boon}} ([[elite]]) * {{skill icon|Ether Prism}} (elite) *{{Skill icon|Signet of Recall}}
== Notes ==
* Can be combined with a [[List of enchantment removal skills#On self|self-enchantment-removal skill]] (e.g. [[Contemplation of Purity]]) to quickly replenish energy. * An [[of Enchanting]] weapon upgrade will delay the energy gain, since it extends the duration of the mantra. * If the mantra is renewed (for any reason) before it ends, the duration is reset; the caster ''will not'' gain any energy.
== Trivia == * This is the only [[Mantra]] that is not a [[Stance]].
