== Notes == * As with any [[doublecast skill]], [[NPC]]s will use this skill as soon as there is an enemy within the spell's [[area of effect]] range of an ally. * Foes suffer two damage [[packet]]s if the caster is targeted; the skill also recharges 50% faster (in effect, the second packet hits a hexed target, triggering the effect). * As this is a ''Hex Spell'' that can ''target an ally'', [[Holy Veil]] will double this skill's casting time when it is used on a target enchanted with it, despite the fact that this ally will not be hexed.
