== Notes == *There are no traps, nor any ranger skills, that apply cracked armor. *Damage is dealt in two [[packet]]s. First the trap is triggered and deals unconditional damage, then the second packet is dealt only to enemies who have cracked armor. If an enemy is in a [[Well of Ruin]] when the trap is triggered, the initial damage will inflict cracked armor, causing the bonus damage to trigger as well.
== Trivia == *The figure in the [[skill icon]] appears to be a male necromancer wearing [[Necromancer Cabal armor|Cabal armor]]. [[Category:Easily interrupted skills]]

