{{Pveversion|Preservation}} {{Skill infobox | name = Preservation (PvP) | id = 3011 | campaign = Factions | profession = Ritualist | attribute = Restoration Magic | type = Binding Ritual | elite = y | energy = 5 | activation = 3 | recharge = 20 | causes1 = Spirit | causes2 = Healing | description = [[Elite]] [[Binding Ritual]]. Create a level {{gr|1|10}} [[spirit]]. Every 4 seconds, this spirit [[heal]]s one non-spirit [[ally]] [[in the area]] for {{gr|10|115}} Health. This spirit dies after 90 seconds. | concise description = Elite Binding Ritual. Creates a level {{gr|1|10}} Spirit (90 second lifespan). Every 4 seconds this spirit heals one non-spirit ally for {{gr|10|115}}. | is-pvp = y | aoe = in the area }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Restoration Magic]] | var1 name = Level | var1 at0 = 1 | var1 at15 = 10 | var2 name = [[Heal]]ing | var2 at0 = 10 | var2 at15 = 115}}
== Notes == * This skill creates a [[Spirit of Preservation]]. * The spirit heals one random ally in the area, including allies with full health. * The healing is a passive effect; the spirit does not use any skills, so it cannot be [[interrupt]]ed; however, the healing will still trigger [[Scourge Healing]].
== Trivia == * The [[skill icon]] for this skill shows a figure holding a glowing [[w:Ankh|ankh]], the Egyptian symbol of life.
