__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 103 | name = Price of Failure | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Necromancer | attribute = Curses | type = Hex Spell | energy = 15 | activation = 2 | recharge = 20 | causes1 = Miss | description = [[Hex Spell]]. For 30 seconds, [[target]] [[foe]] has a 25% chance to [[miss]] with [[attack]]s and takes {{gr|1|46}} [[damage]] whenever that foe fails to hit in combat. | concise description = Hex Spell. (30 seconds.) 25% chance to miss. Target foe takes {{gr|1|46}} damage whenever it fails to hit. }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Curses]] | var1 name = [[Damage]] | var1 at0 = 1 | var1 at15 = 46}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]s''' * [[The Lost Princess]] ([[Fishermen's Haven]]) '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Bartoch]] ([[Droknar's Forge]]) * [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]]) '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Geck the Coldblooded]] ([[North Kryta Province]]) * [[Gambol the Headrainer]] ([[Nebo Terrace]]) * [[Skigg the Tongue]] ([[D'Alessio Seaboard]]) * [[Eepeep the Mindrain]] ([[Watchtower Coast]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Reckless Haste}} * {{skill icon|Spirit of Failure}}
== Notes == * This skill triggers when the target [[Fail#Skills that have an effect when an attack fails to hit|fails to hit]], for ''whatever'' reason. Hence, [[block]]ing with a skill, simply [[Line of sight|dodging a ranged attack, or even using the terrain to avoid being hit]] by a [[ranged attack]] will trigger the damage. * Combine with skills that causes [[Blind]]ness to increase the miss chance and improve damage rate. * This skill can be combined with [[Spirit of Failure]] as each will cause the foe to miss more often, thereby triggering both effects more frequently than either alone; however, hexes that make the target "miss" combine multiplicatively and not additively. Thus, a foe hexed with both [[Reckless Haste]] and Price of Failure has a 62.5% chance to miss with attacks.
== Trivia == * The skull on the [[skill icon]] looks like the one on [[Consume Corpse]] and [[Enfeeble]].
[[Category:Necromancer skill rewards]] [[Category:Armor-ignoring damage]]

