== Notes == * This skill creates a [[Spirit of Quickening Zephyr]]. * The cost increase occurs at the beginning of the activation of a skill, while the recharge reduction occurs at the end. * The reduced recharge stacks multiplicatively with [[Fast Casting]] in [[PvE]], for up to 74% recharge time reduction for [[Mesmer]] spells. * Quickening Zephyr can reduce its own recharge time from rank 11 onwards, but it has to be under its own effect first. ** Having another party member carry the skill or using [[Echo]] works. ** Primary ranger can also achieve this on their own with a combination of 16 Wilderness Survival and [[Serpent's Quickness]]. ** Non-primary rangers (Ritualists for instance) can also use [[Serpent's Quickness]] with [[consumable]]s or [[Heroic Refrain]] to reach rank 16. * The energy skill cost increase is rounded down from 0.5. The following table shows the energy skill cost increases in the presence of a Quickening Zephyr: :{| {{STDT}} |- align="center" style="background:lightgray;" !Base cost ! width="12px"| 1 || width="12px"| 5 || width="12px"| 10 || width="12px"| 15 || width="12px"| 25 |- align="center" |Increase | 0 || 1 || 3 || 4 || 7 |- align="center" |Total cost | 1 || 6 || 13 || 19 || 32 |}
