== Notes == * This skill creates a [[Spirit of Recovery]]. * Recovery will reduce the duration of burning on spirits, including itself. {{Bug|The French translation of [[Spirit of Recovery]] is the same as [[Spirit of Recuperation]] but with a lower case "r", which can be misleading.}} {{anomaly|Rather than conditions expiring at a faster rate, their duration is reduced by the stated percentage.}}
