{{Skill infobox | id = 848 | name = Reverse Hex | campaign = Factions | profession = Monk | attribute = Protection Prayers | type = Enchantment Spell | energy = 10 | activation = {{1/4}} | recharge = 10 | causes1 = Damage Reduction | description = [[Enchantment Spell]]. Remove one [[hex]] from [[target]] [[ally]]. If a hex was removed in this way, for {{gr|5|10|}} seconds, the next time target ally would take [[damage]], that damage is [[Damage reduction|reduced]] by {{gr|5|50}}. | concise description = Enchantment Spell. ({{gr|5|10|}} seconds.) Removes one hex from target ally. The next damage this ally takes is reduced by {{gr|5|50}}. {{gray|No effect unless this ally is hexed.}} | target = allies | removes1 = Hex spell }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Protection Prayers]] | var1 name = [[Duration]] | var1 at0 = 5 | var1 at15 = 10 | var2 name = [[Damage reduction]] | var2 at0 = 5 | var2 at15 = 50}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]]) * [[Akane]] ([[Senji's Corner]]) * [[Yokuni]] ([[Maatu Keep]]) * [[Zytka]] ([[House zu Heltzer]])
== Notes == * Reverse Hex is one of the few [[List of hex removal skills|hex removal skills]] that have an [[activation time]] of {{1/4}} second, so this skill can be cast during the [[aftercast delay]] between a hex and its [[cover]] hex, removing it before it is covered.
== Trivia == * The functionality of this skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[/Skill history|skill revision history]] for details.

