== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Factions]] ** [[Spiritroot Mossbeard]] ([[The Eternal Grove (explorable area)]]) ** [[Whispering Ritual Lord]] ([[Silent Surf]]) * [[Eye of the North]] ** [[Glacial Griffon]] (only during [[Cold as Ice]])
