== Notes == * This skill can be used while activating a Binding Ritual, since it does not have an activation time.
* Heroes use this skill whenever they are in combat and a binding ritual is off cooldown. They will not use any non-ritual skills while Ritual Lord is up, waiting for it to expire on its own.
{{anomaly|Ritual Lord will only increase the skill progression of a skill, and not inherent effects from Spawning Power.}}
== Trivia == * This is the only [[unlock]]able non-signet skill that costs neither energy nor adrenaline. * This skill has the lowest [[health]] loss of all skills indicating a [[sacrifice]] cost. * The functionality of this skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[Ritual Lord/Skill history|skill history]] for details.
