{{Skill infobox | id = 884 | name = Searing Flames | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Elementalist | attribute = Fire Magic | type = Spell | elite = y | energy = 15 | activation = 1 | recharge = 2 | target = foes | range = Casting | aoe = nearby | causes1 = Fire Damage | causes2 = Burning | description = [[Elite]] [[Spell]]. [[Target]] [[foe]] and all [[nearby]] foes are struck with Searing Flames. Foes already [[Burning|on fire]] when this skill is cast are struck for {{gr|10|100}} [[fire damage]]. Foes not already on fire begin Burning for {{gr|1|7}} seconds. | concise description = Elite Spell. Hits foes near your target. Deals {{gr|10|100}} fire damage to foes already Burning. Inflicts Burning condition ({{gr|1|7}} seconds) to foes not Burning. }}
