== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Kormab, Burning Heart]] ([[Dasha Vestibule]]) ** [[Korr, Living Flame]] ([[Turai's Procession]]) ** [[Korshek the Immolated]] ([[Forum Highlands]]) * [[Eye of the North]] ** [[Borrguus Blisterbark]] ([[Sacnoth Valley]])
== Notes == * Consider using [[Fire Attunement]], [[Glowing Gaze]], and [[Glyph of Lesser Energy]] to compensate for this spell's high energy cost. * Under [[Glyph of Immolation]], burning is applied to the target before the condition is checked for, so damage will be applied to target. Nearby foes will only suffer burning. ** [[Intensity]] can be used to perform half-damage to foes around target in addition to the previous action. * If your target dies while you are casting Searing Flames, the spell will not [[fail]].
