{{Skill infobox | id = 1088 | name = Second Wind | campaign = Factions | profession = Elementalist | type = Spell | energy = 5 | recharge = 5 | activation = 1 | overcast = 5 | elite = y | causes1 = Energy Gain | causes2 = Health Gain | removes1 = Enchantment | description = [[Elite]] [[Spell]]. You [[Health gain|gain]] 1 [[Energy]] and 5 [[Health]] for each point of Energy restricted by [[Overcast]]. You lose all [[enchantment]]s. | concise description = Elite Spell. You gain 1 Energy and 5 Health for each point of Overcast. You lose all enchantments. }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Snapjaw Windshell]] ([[Archipelagos]])
