== Notes == *This is a [[core]] skill, but [[Guild Wars Factions]] is required to obtain the skill. * The attribute reduction effect persists if the caster dies. * With at least rank 14 [[Critical Strikes]], Shadow Theft will push the Critical Strikes attribute over rank 18 which is the threshold to gain 4 energy per [[critical hit]]. {{bug|This skill will not increase attributes which don't have at ''least'' one point invested in them.}}
