==Notes== *The damage is delivered in three independent packets. Adjacent foes are hit three times, nearby foes twice, and foes in the area only once. **One-time [[damage reduction]] skills, such as [[Reversal of Fortune]], and damage cappers, such [[Protective Spirit]], do not fully protect against this skill, however skills that protect against multiple packets, such as [[Union]], are more effective. **[[Pain Inverter]] will deal damage back for each packet. *Cracked Armor is applied before any damage. {{anomaly|The skill description implies that Blind [[cover]]s Cracked Armor which covers Weakness, while in actuality Blind covers Weakness which covers Cracked Armor.}}
