== Notes == * This skill will affect both targeted enchantments targeted at the caster as well as all [[Target#Untargeted skills|untargeted skills]] (which include party-wide enchantments such as [[Aegis]]). ** Combines well with [[Mystic Healing]] and [[Orders build]] skills. ** Consider using this signet to cast [[Eternal Aura]] instantly to [[resurrect]] allies in mid-battle. * Even though enchantments are made to cast instantly, they are still [[Skill queue|queued]] and cannot be cast while [[Movement|moving]], [[knock down|knocked down]] etc.
