== Notes == * As a [[punish]]ment hex, this skill is more effective in [[Hard mode]] since enemies have faster casting and are thus able to cast more often. * Unlike [[Backfire]], the [[AI]] will cast until death while under the effects of this hex. * Enemies in Hard mode will not use this skill on primary caster professions, or martial professions wielding a staff or wand. They will cast it on martial professions wielding a martial weapon, holding a bundle, or with empty hands.
