{{skill infobox | name = Stout-Hearted | campaign = Eye of the North | attribute = Deldrimor rank | type = Title | causes1 = Health Gain | description = [[Title (skill type)|Title]]. Whenever you use a [[skill]] against a [[Destroyer]], it takes {{gr2|5|15}} [[damage]] and you [[Health gain|gain]] {{gr2|5|15}} [[Health]]. | concise description = Title. Whenever you use a skill against a Destroyer, it takes {{gr2|5|15}} damage and you gain {{gr2|5|15}} Health. }}
{{Skill progression max10 |title track = [[Deldrimor rank]] |var1 name = [[Damage]] |var1 at0 = 5 |var1 at10 = 15 |var2 name = [[Health gain]] |var2 at0 = 5 |var2 at10 = 15 }}
==Acquisition== *Talk to [[Kodan]] [Dwarven Recruitment Officer] in [[Gunnar's Hold]] after attaining the first rank of the [[Deldrimor rank|Deldrimor title]].
==Notes== *This cannot be equipped on the [[skill bar]]. While a [[character]] displays the Deldrimor title, this effect is applied to that character and all of their [[hero]]es. *The skill's damage is not [[life stealing]], but is either armor-ignoring untyped damage (possibly [[chaos damage]] or [[dark damage]]) or direct [[health loss]]. *Stout-Hearted works on any successful skill activation, including [[block]]ed and [[fail]]ed [[attack skill]]s. *This skill affects whatever destroyer you have selected when activating a skill. The skill itself does not need to actually interact with the destroyer in any way to trigger Stout Hearted. For example, using [[Animate Bone Horror]] with a destroyer targeted will work.

