== Notes == * This skill will [[shadow step]] your pet to a target [[ally]] (or even to yourself); this also activates the skill's effect, allowing you to ''prep'' before engaging the enemy. ** Your animal companion must be alive to use this skill. ** You must be within [[casting range]] of your target, although your pet can be farther away.
