{{Skill infobox | id = 551 | name = Stun on Critical Hit | campaign = Core | type = Skill | profession = Monster | special = Passive | special2 = Monster | description = ([[monster]] only) | concise description = (monster only) }}
== Notes == * ''Stun'' is an internal name for [[knock down]]. * Common on [[Giant]]s, [[Wallow]]s, and [[Wurm]]s. ** Consider bringing [[Critical hit#Related skills|skills that prevent critical hits]], but keep in mind that several only prevent extra damage from criticals, not bonus effects like stun. * This skill is a [[passive]], continuously active effect, making it invisible to players.
