__NOTOC__{{Skill infobox | id = 423 | name = Symbiotic Bond | campaign = Prophecies | profession = Ranger | attribute = Beast Mastery | type = Shout | energy = 10 | recharge = 55 | causes1 = Health Regeneration | description = [[Shout]]. For {{gr|120|300}} seconds, your [[animal companion]] gains {{gr|1|3}} [[Health regeneration]], and half of all [[damage]] dealt to your animal companion is redirected to you. | concise description = Shout. ({{gr|120|300}} seconds.) Your pet has +{{gr|1|3}} Health regeneration. Half of all damage dealt to your pet is redirected to you. | aoe = None }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Beast Mastery]] | var1 name = [[Duration]] | var1 at0 = 120 | var1 at15 = 300 | var2 name = [[Health regeneration]] | var2 at0 = 1 | var2 at15 = 3 }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Steig]] ([[Camp Rankor]]) * [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]])
== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Life Bond}} * {{skill icon|Never Rampage Alone}}
== Notes == * The damage redirected to the user is calculated ''after'' the pet's armor, but ''before'' other [[damage reduction]] (by skills like [[Call of Protection]]). If you use this skill and you're taking too much damage, consider +[[armor rating]] skills for your pet rather than +damage reduction. * If [[Balthazar's Spirit]] is also on the user, the energy gain triggers each time the pet takes damage. * Being a shout, you can't end it if you're taking too much damage. * The damage dealt to the user is typeless. {{bug|Upon reconnecting from a disconnect when having this skill active it will appear as a [[Enchantment_spell#Maintained_enchantments|maintained enchantment]]. (See the [[Talk:Symbiotic_Bond|discussion page]] for more information and screenshots.)}}
== Trivia == * This is the only skill with a recharge of 55 seconds. * This skill has changed since its introduction; see its [[/Skill history|skill revision history]] for details.
