== Notes == * Unlike all other skills that "steal" skills, this does not [[disable]] the corresponding original and instead is placed as a [[skill icon]] in the [[Effects Monitor]]. When you hover over the skill icons of elite spells in the Effects Monitor, their skill descriptions will appear to have effects based on their normal ranks, but the Fast Casting rank will be used when the spells are cast. * All elite spells on your skill bar will use your Fast Casting attribute rank even if they were obtained by other means, such as [[Arcane Mimicry]] or [[Arcane Thievery]]. * If your target does not have an elite skill for you to copy, the secondary effect that makes all elite spells use Fast Casting will still apply. * This skill is on the restricted list for [[Codex Arena]].
