{{Skill infobox | id = 152 | name = Taste of Death | campaign = Core | profession = Necromancer | attribute = Death Magic | type = Spell | energy = 5 | activation = {{1/4}} | target = minions | range = Casting | aoe = none | causes1 = Life Stealing | description = [[Spell]]. [[Life stealing|Steal]] up to {{gr|100|400}} [[Health]] from [[target]] [[Minion|animated undead]] [[ally]]. | concise description = Spell. Steals {{gr|100|400}} Health from allied undead servant. }}
{{Skill progression |attribute = [[Death Magic]] |var1 name = [[Life stealing]] |var1 at0 = 100 |var1 at15 = 400 }}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill trainer]]s''' * [[Prophecies]] ** [[Captain Greywind]] ([[North Kryta Province]]) ** [[Master Scout Kiera]] ([[Henge of Denravi]]) ** [[Dakk]] ([[Ember Light Camp]]) * [[Factions]] ** [[Michiko]] ([[Kaineng Center]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Baram]] ([[The Kodash Bazaar]]) '''[[Hero skill trainer]]s''' * Nightfall ** [[Warden of Whispers (Chantry of Secrets)|Warden of Whispers]] ([[Chantry of Secrets]])
== Notes == * As with all life stealing, this skill can only [[heal]] you for the amount of health that the target has left. As such, be sure you target a minion with plenty of health if you need the healing effect. * Can be combined with [[Death Nova]], although [[Putrid Flesh]] may be preferred in that regard. * The health of minions follows the formula health=level*20+80, so the life stealing is a guaranteed kill on minions with level equal to your level of Death Magic+1. ** Assuming a caster both summons the minion and steals health from it, and stays at the same Death Magic rank while doing so, the minion is guaranteed to die if it was a [[jagged horror]] or a [[bone minion]]. Any other minion (except [[Star Servant]] or [[Flesh Golem]]) will die if the caster is at rank 7 or less in Death Magic, and be left with maximum 20 health at higher ranks. [[Flesh Golem]]s will lose around 70% of their health. *** Can be used with [[Jagged Bones]] as a steady source of jagged horrors. *** Using [[Aura of the Lich]] will spawn a [[bone horror]] and then increase the Death Magic rank by 1, effectively allowing to kill the summoned bone horror from full health at any Death Magic rank.
