{{Skill infobox | id = 911 | name = Union | campaign = Factions | profession = Ritualist | attribute = Communing | type = Binding Ritual | energy = 15 | activation = {{3/4}} | recharge = 45 | causes1 = Spirit | causes2 = Damage Reduction | description = [[Binding Ritual]]. Create a level {{gr|1|12}} [[spirit]]. Whenever a non-spirit [[ally]] in its [[Spirit range|range]] takes [[damage]] or [[Life stealing|life steal]], it is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage. This spirit dies after {{gr|30|60}} seconds. | concise description = Binding Ritual. Creates a level {{gr|1|12}} spirit ({{gr|30|60}} second lifespan). Whenever a non-spirit ally within range takes damage or life steal, it is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage. | has-pvp = y }}
{{Skill progression | attribute = [[Communing]] | var1 name = Level | var1 at0 = 1 | var1 at15 = 12 | var2 name = [[Duration]] | var2 at0 = 30 | var2 at15 = 60}}
== Acquisition == '''[[Skill quest]]''' * [[Factions]] ** [[Minions Gone Wild]] ([[Sunqua Vale]]) '''[[Profession changer]]s''' * [[Core]] ** [[Profession Changer (NPC)|Profession Changer]] ([[Great Temple of Balthazar]]) * Factions ** [[Senji]] ([[Senji's Corner]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Zuwarah]] ([[Command Post]])
== Notes == * This skill creates a [[Spirit of Union]]. * Often used with [[Displacement]] and [[Shelter]] to provide superior [[damage reduction]]. ** Shelter and Union's effects are applied in the order they're created. For maximum damage reduction, always cast Shelter ''before'' Union. * Also affects allied [[minion]]s, thus making the spirit die almost instantly if there are allied minions taking damage. * [[Armor of Unfeeling]] can be used to reduce the damage taken by this spirit. * If a damage packet deals less than 15 damage, the spirit only takes damage equal to the amount of damage it prevents.
== Trivia == * The [[skill icon]] is very similar to the [[Peace and Harmony]] icon and [[Friends List]] [[menu button]].
