}} ==Related skills== * {{monster skill icon|Jade Brotherhood Bomb}} * {{monster skill icon|Suicide Energy}} * {{monster skill icon|Suicide Health}}
== Notes == * This skill is used by [[Volatile Ooze]]s and [[Hulking Volatile Ooze]]s. * They can be made to waste it against [[summoned creature]]s (e.g. by sending an [[Ebon Vanguard Assassin Support|Ebon Vanguard Assassin]] in first). * [["Can't Touch This!"]] can prevent the use of Unstable Ooze Explosion and other touch skills used by other oozes (such as [[Headbutt]] used by [[Aggressive Ooze]]s and [[Vile Touch]] used by [[Ominous Ooze]]s) on your [[party]] members. * If you are playing with [[hero]]es and/or [[Henchman|henchmen]], they can easily [[wipe]] your party, due to the large [[area of effect]] damage and the tendency of heroes and henchmen to bunch together. Try to prevent them from getting close to your party, and [[Hero flag|flag]] your heroes and henchmen apart to minimize damage.
== Trivia == * This skill's concise description is longer than its description.
