== Acquisition == '''[[Signet of Capture]]''' * [[Factions]] ** [[Kai Shi Jo]] ([[The Undercity (Winds of Change)]], only during [[When Kappa Attack]]) * [[Nightfall]] ** [[Ensign Jahan]] ([[Cliffs of Dohjok]], only during [[A Land of Heroes]]) ** [[Corsair Commander (dervish)|Corsair Commander]] ([[Dajkah Inlet]]) ** [[Captain Mhedi]] ([[Barbarous Shore]])
