== Notes == * Synergizes well with [[attack skill]]s that can cause multiple attacks with a scythe ([[Eremite's Attack]], [[Twin Moon Sweep]], and [[Whirlwind Attack]]) and with [[hex spell]]s that deal damage whenever the hexed foe takes [[physical damage]] ([[Barbs]] and [[Mark of Pain]]). ** When Eremite's Attack or Whirlwind Attack is used, this skill will trigger for each adjacent foe hit. * Because this triggers ''on attack'', you don't actually have to hit for the damage to occur. * The damage from Vow of Strength is inflicted before the damage from your scythe. This is relevant for skills such as [[Reversal of Fortune]] or [[Empathy]]. * Because this damages all "adjacent foes", [[Kite|kiting]] opponents will avoid damage if they have moved away by the time the attack connects. * [[Extend Enchantments]] can be used to maintain this enchantment.
