{{Skill infobox | name = Ward of Weakness | id = 2001 | campaign = Eye of the North | profession = Elementalist | attribute = Earth Magic | type = Ward Spell | energy = 10 | activation = 1 | recharge = 20 | causes1 = Weakness | description = [[Ward Spell]]. You create a Ward of Weakness at your current location. For {{gr|5|20}} seconds, [[foe]]s [[in the area|in this area]] become [[Weakness|Weakened]] for {{gr|5|20}} seconds whenever they take [[elemental damage]]. | concise description = Ward Spell. ({{gr|5|20}} seconds). Inflicts Weakened condition ({{gr|5|20}} seconds) to any foes that take elemental damage in this ward.}}
