== Notes == * This spell does not need to interrupt a foe for the hex to be applied. * If the hex is ended early by any source, the second interrupt will be triggered. This makes Web of Disruption useful with [[Shatter Delusions]] or [[Drain Delusions]]. * Be careful giving this skill to [[hero]]es, as they treat it as a regular hex and will use it on foes who aren't using any skills. {{anomaly|This skill's standard description does not specify whether it can interrupt only skills or all [[action]]s, including attacks. The effect is clarified in the concise description which states that both the initial and ending interrupts only affect skills.}}
