{{Skill infobox | name = Wielder's Remedy | id = 1740 | campaign = Nightfall | profession = Ritualist | attribute = Spawning Power | type = Enchantment Spell | energy = 5 | activation = 1 | recharge = 10 | description = [[Enchantment Spell]]. For {{gr|10|30}} seconds, whenever you cast a [[weapon spell]] on an [[ally]], that ally loses 1 [[condition]]. | concise description = Enchantment Spell. ({{gr|10|30}} seconds.) Whenever you cast a weapon spell, the targeted ally loses one condition. | removes1 = Condition | target = self }}
