== Game mechanics == * This enchantment spell can be maintained at 0 spawning power, i.e. it can be used effectively by non-primary ritualist characters. ** Does not work with [[Weapon of Aggression]], since it only self-targets. ** Does not work with [[Weapons of Three Forges]], since it does not target an ally.
