== Related skills == * {{skill icon|Wielder's Zeal}} ([[elite]])
== Notes == * The shortest recharging weapon spell (with a recharge time of 1s) is [[Ghostly Weapon]]. Since the rank in [[Communing]] affects only Ghostly Weapon's duration, it can be used effectively even at 0 Communing. Other short recharging item spells are [[Vital Weapon]] (2s), [[Vengeful Weapon]] , [[Weapon of Remedy]] and [[Xinrae's Weapon]] (3s). The activation time is of 1/4s for all those skills but Vital Weapon (1s). Other weapon spells that synergizes with Wielder's Remedy have a recharge time of at least 5s for a casting time of 1s. [[Category:Skills offered by hero skill trainers]]

