== Notes == * This skill is used by [[Frostmaw the Kinslayer]] and [[Frost Siege Wurm]]s. * This skill can reach across compass range. * It deals 50 [[cold damage]] if it hits its target and 60 cold damage to foes within the area of its impact; the AoE damage decreases with distance, to a minimum of 1 damage at the edge of earshot range.
